<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>PSA_ERROR_GENERIC_ERROR</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>An unspecified internal failure happened. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>PSA_ERROR_INVALID_ARGUMENT</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>One or more arguments are invalid. This can also happen if <computeroutput>data_offset</computeroutput> is larger than the size of the data associated with <computeroutput>uid</computeroutput>. </para>
